                                                            <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                                <p><strong>Love is the answer!</strong></p>
                                                                <p>Through love, life perspective flourishes;
                                                                    you are awakened to what really matters;
                                                                    relationships thrive; you are more alert,
                                                                    thoughtful and sensitive; your perceptions
                                                                    are more accurate; you are more aware of
                                                                    your environment, animals and plants that
                                                                    surround your life; you prosper simply
                                                                    because you are focusing on love and
                                                                    gratitude; life transcends beyond your
                                                                    wildest dreams; and, the Spirit within
                                                                    cultivates as a new you emerges and
                                                                    blossoms.</p>
